profile:
Our Clients are #1 priority so we truly believe in high business ethics as far as relations with our clients are concerned. We strongly intend to develop a closer trust based on a long-term business relationship with our clients. Equally important to us is that our quality of products delivered matches the quality of our service. Our furniture is well maintained and spotless. If an item in our collection is damaged, ripped, broken or stained… it does NOT leave our showroom.
When you team up with Stagers Choice, you get more than a catalog of fine furniture, you get a team of professionals willing to go beyond to help you with your project and make your experience with us efficient & profitable.

We have flexible prices & lease terms and delivery all over GTA is available within 24 hours.

profile:
Rooms in Bloom Home Staging & Design Inc. are Kitchener-Waterloo's Home Staging experts and we specialize in transforming spaces to attract your home's target buyers. We are your real estate marketing edge and the key to adding tangible value your buyers will appreciate.

Specializing in staging vacant properties as well as builder model and spec homes, we understand that people are looking not just for a house, but for a lifestyle they aspire to have. With over eight years experience and hundreds of homes staged, we provide cutting edge home staging services that improve the overall presentation and marketability of properties every day.

Contact our multi-award winning team today to get the Rooms in Bloom Advantage! Our experienced RE Marketing Consultants will help make your home THE property buyers want to purchase! (519) 804-STAGE
